title: 029 - Drafting Your Movie Character Seal Team 6
description: On today's show, the guys discuss some of the new things coming to Netflix here soon, their thoughts on Waco, and they also do a snake draft to complete their Seal Team 6 with movie characters. Keep sending in questions to @ThePodPMI on Twitter and Instagram, and have a safe weekend. Enjoy.
